			"tradition":"Sorcery, Witchcraft",
			"description":"The mystic masters the stare of the Evil Eye and can curse enemies on the battlefield; a power often used by the disciples of the Dark Lords during The Great War.",
			"novice":"<span class='text-success'>Novice</span> Free. Once per turn, the mystic's dark glare automatically gives an enemy a second chance to fail all success tests meant to affect the mystic (roll twice, the action fails if one of the tests is a failure). This effect is ongoing until the mystic fails a Resolute test.",
