			"adepte":"<span class='text-info'>Adept</span> Active. Pass a Resolute test to become invisible to all nearby enemies, until attacking or taking damage.",
			"maitre":"<span class='text-danger'>Master</span> Active. With a successful Resolute test, the mystic can make itself and an ally fade from the perception of their enemies. The mystic and the ally remain invisible separately and can be detected or remain hidden separately, until they make an attack or take any kind of damage."
		},
