		"en_31":{
			"novice":"The weapon is instilled with storming, thunderous energies. Each hit echoes with the powers of lightning. If any of the damage penetrates the armor, the target also has to pass a Strong test or lose an active or movement action because of the force unleashed by the Thundering hit."
		},
		"en":{
