			"novice":"I Free. The creature spreads the paralyzing cold of the grave; player characters within melee distance are paralyzed, should they fail a Resolute test. One test is made each turn, and should the test be successful, the character can act as normal. Once a character has withstood the cold of the grave it cannot be affected again during the same scene.",
			"adepte":"II Free. As I, but with the addition that the cold is harmful, dealing 2 points of damage per turn to those affected, ignoring Armor.",
